data.description: Don't miss this wonderful property in the heart of Paradise Hills. Three bedroom home that could easily be turned into a 6 bedroom home & 3 bathrooms. Convenient to shopping, restaurants and other amenities. A beautiful sunroom welcomes you to this light filled beauty! Lots of living space to spread out.  Updates throughout. Large backyard to enjoy all year around! Don't miss the mountain views to the east. Come tour this home today!
